         Instant cast invis means that you can refresh invis while in the middle of mobs.</P><P>Instant cast invis means that you can cast it while running.</P><P>Instant cast invis means that you can use it to go invis while root dotting, which is pretty handy in keeping the yard trash and roamers off of your back.</P><P></P><P> <a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
